fig_pie = plt.figure(figsize=(8,8))

house_type = house_data[''].unique()
num1 = house_data[''][house_data[''] == ''].count()
num2 = house_data[''][house_data[''] == ''].count()
num_type = [num1, num2]

plt.rcParams['text.color'] = 'Navy'  # Label color
a, b = [plt.cm.Blues, plt.cm.Reds]
plt.pie(num_type, labels = house_type, colors = [a(0.6), b(0.6)], 
        autopct='%.2f',
        wedgeprops = { 'linewidth' : 7, 'edgecolor' : 'white' }, 
        textprops={'fontsize': 18})

plt.show()
